<section class="py-24 bg-white" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h6 class="text-lg text-yellow-600 font-medium mb-2">FAQs</h6>
      <h2 id="faq-heading" class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-[3.25rem] font-manrope">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 hover:bg-yellow-50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 group-open:text-yellow-600 group-hover:text-yellow-600">
          <span>Do I have to pay for the consultation?</span>
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-2xl text-gray-500 group-hover:text-yellow-600">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-5 pt-1 text-base text-gray-700 leading-6">
          Nope. Your first consultation is 100% free. We'll help you understand your options and give you a personalized migration plan—no strings attached.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 hover:bg-yellow-50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 group-open:text-yellow-600 group-hover:text-yellow-600">
          <span>Is this a visa agency?</span>
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-2xl text-gray-500 group-hover:text-yellow-600">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-5 pt-1 text-base text-gray-700 leading-6">
          Not exactly. We're a guidance platform that helps you prepare your application to increase your chances of success, whether it's a visa, a study program, or a relocation.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 hover:bg-yellow-50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 group-open:text-yellow-600 group-hover:text-yellow-600">
          <span>Can I apply even if I don't have a university degree?</span>
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-2xl text-gray-500 group-hover:text-yellow-600">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-5 pt-1 text-base text-gray-700 leading-6">
          Yes! Many programs value experience, motivation, and skills. During the consultation, we’ll explore which pathways suit your current situation.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 hover:bg-yellow-50 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 group-open:text-yellow-600 group-hover:text-yellow-600">
          <span>What countries can I apply to with your help?</span>
          <span class="transform transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45 text-2xl text-gray-500 group-hover:text-yellow-600">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-5 pt-1 text-base text-gray-700 leading-6">
          We specialize in destinations like Canada, Australia, Germany, and New Zealand, but our network expands to over 10 countries depending on your profile.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
